## 💾 Backing Up Your Characters

Before doing anything major — back up your character data:

```bash
docker exec wow-server-ac-database-1 mysqldump \
    -uroot -ppassword \
    --databases acore_characters acore_auth acore_world \
    > ~/wow-backup-$(date +%Y%m%d).sql
```

This saves everything to a file named with today's date.
Keep this file somewhere safe!

**To restore a backup:**
```bash
docker exec -i wow-server-ac-database-1 \
    mysql -uroot -ppassword \
    < ~/wow-backup-YYYYMMDD.sql
```

